name: clustered_data_warehouse
description: This project was made to help analyze foreign exchange (FX) deals. It includes features for importing and validating deal details, ensuring no duplicates, and storing valid deals in a PostgreSQL database. The application is easy to deploy with Docker Compose and includes thorough unit tests to ensure everything works smoothly.
